Package com.flipkart.bean

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.Booking
public class Booking extends Object
The Booking class represents a booking made by a user for a specific time slot in a gym. Contains details such as booking ID, user ID, slot ID, booking date and time, status, transaction ID, and amount.

      public Booking(int bookingId, int userId, int slotId, String bookingDate, String bookingTimeSlotStart, String bookingTimeSlotEnd, int bookingStatus, int transactionId, int bookingAmount)
      Constructor to initialize a Booking object with all fields.
      Parameters:
      bookingId - the unique identifier for the booking
      userId - the ID of the user who made the booking
      slotId - the ID of the slot that was booked
      bookingDate - the date when the booking was made
      bookingTimeSlotStart - the start time of the booking
      bookingTimeSlotEnd - the end time of the booking
      bookingStatus - the status of the booking
      transactionId - the ID of the transaction associated with the booking
      bookingAmount - the amount paid for the booking
